including Saturday Night at the Mill, Ask Aspel, the Leo Sayer show and
Wogan, as well as Top of the Pops. This compilation showcases her
performances of hit songs such as Wuthering Heights, Babooshka, Running
up That Hill and Hounds of Love alongside other intriguing and lesser
known material in the BBC studios.
